---
layout: page.njk
title: Visiting Aberdeen
subtitle: Welcome to Aberdeen, Maryland — your Home of Opportunity in the heart of the Mid-Atlantic.
description: Visitor information for Aberdeen, Maryland — attractions, transportation, first responders, and local resources.
breadcrumb:
  - label: Visitors
---

<div class="space-y-10">

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
    <div>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">Aberdeen, Maryland is conveniently located in the prime Mid-Atlantic region — just 26 miles northeast of Baltimore, with easy access to Washington DC, Wilmington, Delaware, and Philadelphia.</p>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Whether you're visiting for business, recreation, or to explore our history, Aberdeen offers a warm welcome. The City is home to Aberdeen Proving Ground, a vibrant downtown Main Street, and beautiful parks and open spaces.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-gov-blue-light rounded-xl p-6">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy mb-4">Getting Here</h2>
      <dl class="space-y-3 text-sm">
        <div><dt class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">By Train</dt><dd class="text-slate-700">MARC Penn Line — direct service from Baltimore &amp; Washington DC to Aberdeen Station</dd></div>
        <div><dt class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">By Car</dt><dd class="text-slate-700">I-95 Exit 85 (MD Route 22) — 26 miles northeast of Baltimore</dd></div>
        <div><dt class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">Nearest Airport</dt><dd class="text-slate-700">Baltimore/Washington International (BWI) — approx. 45 minutes</dd></div>
      </dl>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy mb-6">Things to Do &amp; See</h2>
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
      {% for item in [
        { title: "Aberdeen Proving Ground", desc: "The US Army's foremost research and technology center — a cornerstone of Aberdeen's identity and economy." },
        { title: "Aberdeen Main Street", desc: "Historic downtown district with shops, dining, and year-round community events and festivals." },
        { title: "Ripken Stadium", desc: "Home of the Aberdeen IronBirds, a Minor League Baseball affiliate — family-friendly games all summer." },
        { title: "City Parks", desc: "Aberdeen's network of parks and green spaces offer recreation for all ages, including Festival Park." },
        { title: "Aberdeen Activity Center", desc: "Community recreation facility at 7 Franklin Street with fitness and programs for residents and visitors." },
        { title: "Heritage & History", desc: "Explore Aberdeen's 250-year history through the Heritage Trust Committee's events and landmarks." }
      ] %}
      <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-5">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-navy mb-2">{{ item.title }}</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">{{ item.desc }}</p>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy mb-6">Upcoming Events</h2>
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      {% for event in events.community %}
      <a href="{{ event.url }}" class="flex items-center gap-4 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-4 hover:border-amber-400 hover:shadow-sm transition-all duration-200 group">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-500 text-white rounded-lg flex flex-col items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-center leading-none">
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold opacity-80 uppercase">{{ event.month }}</span>
          <span class="text-lg font-bold">{{ event.day }}</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-sm font-bold text-navy group-hover:text-amber-600 transition-colors duration-200">{{ event.title }}</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5">{{ event.location }}</div>
        </div>
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    <div class="mt-4"><a href="{{ '/events/' | url }}" class="text-gov-blue font-semibold hover:underline text-sm">All events →</a></div>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">First Responders</h2>
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
      <a href="{{ '/departments/police/' | url }}" class="flex items-center gap-4 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-5 hover:border-gov-blue hover:shadow-sm transition-all duration-200 group">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-gov-blue-light flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-gov-blue transition-colors duration-200 flex-shrink-0">
          <svg aria-hidden="true" class="w-5 h-5 text-gov-blue group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-200" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M2.166 4.999A11.954 11.954 0 0010 1.944 11.954 11.954 0 0017.834 5c.11.65.166 1.32.166 2.001 0 5.225-3.34 9.67-8 11.317C5.34 16.67 2 12.225 2 7c0-.682.057-1.35.166-2.001zm11.541 3.708a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
        </div>
